import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';

import {  Grid, Icon} from 'semantic-ui-react'

const _BrowseCategories = () => {

    return (
        <Grid columns='equal' textAlign="center" className="CustomtransientUp">
            <Grid.Column>
                <Icon name="line graph" color="olive" />Trends Now
        </Grid.Column>
            <Grid.Column>
                <Icon name="fire" color="orange" />Poupular
        </Grid.Column>
            <Grid.Column>
                <Icon name="bullhorn" color="teal" />Promotions
        </Grid.Column>
            <Grid.Column>
                <Icon name="film" color="green" />Showtimes
        </Grid.Column>
            <Grid.Column>
                <Icon name="calendar check outline" color="blue" />Bookings
        </Grid.Column>
        </Grid>

    )
}


export default _BrowseCategories;
